  "name": "RPlog_Swoop_Fight",
  "title": "Blood Alley Swoop War",
  "summary": "Holed up in the fortified Side Deck on a war-torn Nar Shaddaa, an unlikely band gathers as hired swoop gangs close in to kill them. The Sith Tyler Damion, operating as 'Tatooine Bob,' rallies the group, which includes the cocky Imperial traitor Dareus, the surgeon Lynae, the crimson Twi'lek Ka'una, her companion Via, the Wookiee Joworral, the dying doctor Xar'on, the deck's proprietor Kaitlin, the pirate captain Juran, the soldier Sarray, and the New Republic pair Lon and Siren. After arming up and improvising incendiary 'Side Specials,' the group mounts swoops and rides out to meet the Dug gang leader Unb'tar, whose Thrashers give chase through the vertical city's canyons. A furious running swoop battle ensues, with Tyler leaping between bikes with his lightsaber, Dareus blazing away from the back of Tyler's swoop, Ka'una slicing enemy riders apart with twin vibroblades while Lynae drives, and Kaitlin and Eithne hurling grenades and gunfire. The Thrashers are wiped out, but a second, angrier gang, the Slashers led by Ander Dar, ambushes the survivors with grenade launchers. The heroes prevail again at heavy cost, ending with Tyler/Malign telekinetically destroying Ander's swoop and the battered band regrouping in Blood Alley.",
